    <div class="main review-item" id="1621076">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1621076/" class="title-link">现在的出版人画蛇添足</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1621076"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1123727-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Elact</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-01-16"
      class="main-meta">2009-01-16 08:50:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1621076_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  原来的冰鉴就很薄很薄的一小本。  现在的出版人滥竽充数，给每一句曾国藩语录都加上很多案例，把书弄成厚厚一本，然后索取高价。  而且很多案例都是驴唇不对马嘴，看了案例，反而分散读者对曾语录的细细揣摩。  仔细说来，就有一句印象最深，“身到、心到、眼到、手到、口到”

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1621076/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">30有用 / 1没用</span>
